Westmoreland Coal Co. Unit
Westmoreland Energy is a developer and owner of
cogeneration and unregulated power plants. Westmoreland Coal,
based in Philadelphia, is a producer of low-sulfur coal. LGE
Power Systems, formerly Hadson Power Systems, develops,
builds, operates and owns electric power generation
facilities. LGE Energy Corp., based in Louisville, Ky., is
an energy services company that also owns Louisville Gas 
Electric Co.
   The financing comes from five financial institutions:
Credit Suisse, Prudential Power Funding Associates, National
Westminster Bank PLC, Bank of Nova Scotia and Sumitomo Bank
Ltd.